</a>
</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/interviews/love-only-story-conversation-mame-bougouma-diene-and-woppa-diallo-darlington">Love Is the Only Story: A Conversation with Mame Bougouma Diene and Woppa…</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/darlington-chibueze-anuonye" hreflang="en">Darlington Chibueze Anuonye</a>
